{"tid":2320430,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇試過幫另一半借錢/借比另一半","createTime":"2020-12-10T21:41:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-11T01:46:53.000Z","uid":270608,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"a80ca056a019ed4c6aa72b2e384e216197a05070","tid":2320430,"uid":270608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T21:41:50.000Z","msg":"望住自己另一半因為錢壓力爆煲個樣 <br />\n點忍心唔理<br />\n知道近排周轉不零<br />\n盡最大力量去體諒<br />\n自己幫到幾多都會去幫<br />\n<br />\n身邊朋友話自己蠢<br />\n為左另一半搞到自己欠債<br />\n<br />\n有時訓唔着都會諗下<br />\n其實自己係咪做錯左<br />\n係咪應該對住自己愛嘅人都做一個自私嘅人先岩<br />\n無助 好大壓力 <br />\n但望住另一半 又唔忍心責怪<br />\n因為你知佢都好辛苦 你都好心痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實講到尾 <br />\n係咪跟本一開始就唔應該借錢比另一半？"},{"pid":"d983ccf9409a8623708858ab4967bec5c427bfe5","tid":2320430,"uid":128102,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T21:44:11.000Z","msg":"錢銀既野親生都要清清楚楚<br />\n(係影響到自己經濟情況既程度下)<br />\n完"},{"pid":"4e133e854752e77687cc41775ee3e04733d23d6b","tid":2320430,"uid":270608,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d983ccf9409a8623708858ab4967bec5c427bfe5","tid":2320430,"uid":128102,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T21:44:11.000Z","msg":"錢銀既野親生都要清清楚楚<br />\n(係影響到自己經濟情況既程度下)<br />\n完"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T21:51:03.000Z","msg":"已經捱到好灰<br />\n當初應承幫佢頂一頂兩個月就會清返條數<br />\n但都做不到 一直拖一直拖<br />\n但又唔可以怪佢<br />\n因為佢都真係無<br />\n唉好煩"},{"pid":"6f539f3fae22e9607e14773833c9375aade6be46","tid":2320430,"uid":132047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T21:51:12.000Z","msg":"因乜事會有錢壓力? 賭 or 供樓?"},{"pid":"5d0abcd69371510d19aad4bd662056f6f63608c7","tid":2320430,"uid":270608,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6f539f3fae22e9607e14773833c9375aade6be46","tid":2320430,"uid":132047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T21:51:12.000Z","msg":"因乜事會有錢壓力? 賭 or 供樓?"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T22:01:40.000Z","msg":"本身做緊嘅工作因疫情暫停<br />\n只可以等 同埋因工作前排賠左一大筆錢<br />\n加上之前本身自己有小欠債+而家每日嘅支岀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6051a97b17481925f3a15854770ab32f61bb8ef7","tid":2320430,"uid":132047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5d0abcd69371510d19aad4bd662056f6f63608c7","tid":2320430,"uid":270608,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6f539f3fae22e9607e14773833c9375aade6be46","tid":2320430,"uid":132047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T21:51:12.000Z","msg":"因乜事會有錢壓力? 賭 or 供樓?"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T22:01:40.000Z","msg":"本身做緊嘅工作因疫情暫停<br />\n只可以等 同埋因工作前排賠左一大筆錢<br />\n加上之前本身自己有小欠債+而家每日嘅支岀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T22:11:43.000Z","msg":"咁人有三衰六旺嘅，但千奇唔好幫佢借銀行 / 財仔，保證實後悔。最多生活上幫佢"},{"pid":"5bb8b9980c18f70455f947f1cfe55b1e2dd22204","tid":2320430,"uid":204242,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5d0abcd69371510d19aad4bd662056f6f63608c7","tid":2320430,"uid":270608,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6f539f3fae22e9607e14773833c9375aade6be46","tid":2320430,"uid":132047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T21:51:12.000Z","msg":"因乜事會有錢壓力? 賭 or 供樓?"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T22:01:40.000Z","msg":"本身做緊嘅工作因疫情暫停<br />\n只可以等 同埋因工作前排賠左一大筆錢<br />\n加上之前本身自己有小欠債+而家每日嘅支岀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T22:14:19.000Z","msg":"點都好，保住條命仔，唔好諗尋短見嗰啲。<br />\n人生仲有好多機會，仲有好多美好嘅事.物<br />\n等緊你去發掘同經歷<br />\n風水輪流轉，你唔會一世都係依家呢個境地/情況。<br />\n你過多兩三年，睇返依家嘅自己/自己嘅遭遇，你會覺得依家經歷嘅嘢真係只係好小事，係完全可以承擔嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n加油 共勉<br />\n其實依家人人都好大壓力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到依家仲未訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ea8c60cf4956114c209fb13989b9186567dcecb","tid":2320430,"uid":204309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5d0abcd69371510d19aad4bd662056f6f63608c7","tid":2320430,"uid":270608,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6f539f3fae22e9607e14773833c9375aade6be46","tid":2320430,"uid":132047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T21:51:12.000Z","msg":"因乜事會有錢壓力? 賭 or 供樓?"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T22:01:40.000Z","msg":"本身做緊嘅工作因疫情暫停<br />\n只可以等 同埋因工作前排賠左一大筆錢<br />\n加上之前本身自己有小欠債+而家每日嘅支岀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T22:18:09.000Z","msg":"你定佢本身有欠債"},{"pid":"460c5efa7f31541e1baebb25f9c51632d6a46450","tid":2320430,"uid":5725,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T22:18:33.000Z","msg":"如果你預左同佢過人世既， 就算叫你捐個肝俾佢續命你都肯架啦<br />\n<br />\n自己諗清楚佢係咪都愛你咪得"},{"pid":"a5dfaaeaf680177c40eae7b8178f426feecf9fd3","tid":2320430,"uid":380071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T22:36:27.000Z","msg":"借唔係問題 但係真係要有借據 日後保障返自己 當初同你一樣 身邊啲人都話我戇鳩 出去借財仔幫佢還錢 寫借據唔代表唔愛佢 但係當分手個陣 佢未必重情義 唔還你就碌撚 我個陣都係唔忍心睇住佢死先借 點知一分手就真係咩都無 還開有條路 一陣佢當係老奉 唔想你好似我咁 借完要講好幾時還  同埋勸樓主真係呢啲嘢可避則避 錢呢樣野真係好影響感情 萬一到時分左手 但係你成身數 對下一個女朋友好唔公平 到時你再拍拖 想同女朋友食好啲 買禮物都要就住就住 無理由要佢同你一齊慳  之後個任知道咗又會有條刺 覺得你可以為左佢犧牲咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果條數都頗大 勸你盡早抽身 最緊要你到時唔好後悔"},{"pid":"0d4e9bf36cecc7aa2aee87c3c9e5e249b9219d66","tid":2320430,"uid":323845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T23:07:26.000Z","msg":"借錢都還好 幫佢借錢就萬萬不能 到時佢唔還大耳窿就煩足你一世 但佢唔還俾你 頂多就冇咗啲錢"},{"pid":"4be2f6c3050da9d8460e8ed31f4cbe2e652cdcec","tid":2320430,"uid":281822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5d0abcd69371510d19aad4bd662056f6f63608c7","tid":2320430,"uid":270608,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6f539f3fae22e9607e14773833c9375aade6be46","tid":2320430,"uid":132047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T21:51:12.000Z","msg":"因乜事會有錢壓力? 賭 or 供樓?"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T22:01:40.000Z","msg":"本身做緊嘅工作因疫情暫停<br />\n只可以等 同埋因工作前排賠左一大筆錢<br />\n加上之前本身自己有小欠債+而家每日嘅支岀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T23:07:30.000Z","msg":"真心長貧難顧<br />\n你有心同佢捱寧願出街行公園都唔好借錢<br />\n<br />\n聽你地兩個收入都一般咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"908e45092dc4319fe17b63134d8cb1a3e663049f","tid":2320430,"uid":172443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T23:11:11.000Z","msg":"過5000就不會借<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />睇樓主你似做左擔保人？"},{"pid":"a566291cd2587aa957dcf067d45050a618b457a5","tid":2320430,"uid":369822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T01:46:53.000Z","msg":"一定一定要講清楚分清楚。同埋唔好幫對方做擔保人。有啲人見你借咗一次就會不停問，唔好心軟讓步。<br />\n<br />\n利申：眼見媽咪俾個仆街老竇10幾年來呃晒啲錢，講起錢上嚟有啲人會不擇手段，希望樓主小心。<br />\n<br />\n變本加厲嘅話我建議你快啲走喇。"}]}